extracted_text: (3) Off-street parking requirements. Two spaces shall be required for each dwelling unit, and spaces for other uses in the R-10M zoning district shall be provided as required in Section 14.11.5 and 14.11.6 of this chapter.
llm_output.rationale: This section specifies the parking requirements for the R-10M Multi-Family Residential district. It states that two spaces are required per dwelling unit.
